5\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/02\/28\/make-me-partner-with-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14606,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: You make me a partner with Allah?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat Allah wills and what you will.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHave you made me a partner with Allah? Rather, what Allah wills alone.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 783 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37278,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/31\/safeguarding-oaths-phrases\/","url_meta":{"origin":14606,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Safeguarding words from lesser idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutaylah reported: A Jewish man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, you are setting up rivals with Allah and associating partners with Him when you say, \u2018What Allah wills and you will,\u2019 and when you swear by the Ka\u2019bah!\u201d Then the Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/allah-displeased-if-no-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":14606,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah displeased with unmindful gatherings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit in a gathering without remembering Allah, or sending blessings upon their Prophet, but that they will earn the displeasure of Allah. If Allah wills, He will punish them. If He wills, He will forgive them.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":14606,"position":4},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/dua-affirm-hearts-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":14606,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Guidance: O Allah, affirm our hearts upon Your religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: \u00a0I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how often you supplicate saying: O Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Umm Salamah, there is no human but that his heart is between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14606","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14606"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14606\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14606"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/w